{"tid":11352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【反方丈霸權】高登仔棄高登！另起爐灶LIHKG 登下載榜首","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:15:08.000Z","uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da0df316cfe5eb240e07f31ceb7c3ce0c053e6a0","tid":11352,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】是咁的，唔少人過去一直透過第三方手機App「HKG+」上高登討論區，貪個App夠順。不過人稱「方丈」嘅高登行政總裁林祖舜，之前決定不再授權「HKG+」作為第三方程式，「HKG+」喺上星期五正式結束服務。慘就慘在，唔少高登仔都狂批官方App太廢！<br />\n<br />\n一石激起千重浪！林祖舜一個決定，令一班高登仔怨氣進一步升溫！「HKG+」於是將部分程式碼交俾有心人去另起爐灶，成立「LIHKG討論區」，上星期五蘋果App Store上架後，旋即成為下載榜首；今日LIHKG亦已喺Android Play Store上架，網頁版也會稍後推出。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本報曾嘗試聯絡林祖舜，但暫未成功聯絡。</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祖舜連影都無埋 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55980247&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55980247%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8dff3718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55980247%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=6ddec2ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55980247&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"}]}